00:36:18,380 --> 00:36:21,710
Traitor! How could you do that? 

460
00:36:21,710 --> 00:36:23,190
Where is it? 

461
00:36:23,190 --> 00:36:25,450
The hotel he worked at briefly before. 

462
00:36:26,170 --> 00:36:31,080
We sang "Happy first day of work" and blew out a candle, too. 

463
00:36:31,080 --> 00:36:34,560
Why? You'll probably quit any day now. 

464
00:36:34,560 --> 00:36:37,150
Don't worry, mother. 

