00:36:37,150 --> 00:36:40,850
I promised Hobak I won't quit this time. 

466
00:36:40,850 --> 00:36:43,710
Lots of great things are happening now. 

467
00:36:43,710 --> 00:36:47,550
I got a job and Minjung moved. 

468
00:36:48,460 --> 00:36:50,050
Are you joking? 

469
00:36:50,730 --> 00:36:52,290
Of course not. 

