495
00:38:07,640 --> 00:38:09,160
I believe in Minjung. 

496
00:38:10,150 --> 00:38:13,310
I'm giving it 3 years. 

497
00:38:13,960 --> 00:38:16,010
We must live here for 3 years? 

498
00:38:16,010 --> 00:38:17,870
You can do it. 

499
00:38:17,870 --> 00:38:19,730
Others live here. 

500
00:38:20,200 --> 00:38:23,920
Who knows?
