00:38:30,060 --> 00:38:32,900
Words mean nothing. 

505
00:38:32,900 --> 00:38:35,210
Oh my poor daughter. 

506
00:38:35,210 --> 00:38:37,870
I raised her as a princess. 

507
00:38:42,480 --> 00:38:44,310
I'm sorry, mom. 

508
00:38:45,520 --> 00:38:48,330
I never wanted you to see this. 

509
00:38:50,860 --> 00:38:53,480
I'm sorry, father. 

