535
00:40:15,230 --> 00:40:17,230
She'll become a better person. 

536
00:40:17,230 --> 00:40:19,500
Are you saying Subak isn't a good person? 

537
00:40:19,500 --> 00:40:22,650
I can't believe my ears! 

538
00:40:22,650 --> 00:40:28,040
She had you take care of her girls and the housekeeper run the house. 

539
00:40:28,040 --> 00:40:31,790
She worked her husband like a slave! 

540
00:40:32,270 --> 00:40:34,670
It's not a crime to have a good life. 

541
00:40:34,670 --> 00:40:36,270
It is. 

542
00:40:36,270 --> 00:40:39,320
When you give birth, you must be a mother. 

543
00:40:39,320 --> 00:40:43,390
She's old but she's a crybaby. 

544
00:40:44,600 --> 00:40:49,770
You tell my mother she spoils Don, 

545
00:40:49,770 --> 00:40:51,950
but you're no different. 

546
00:40:52,400 --> 00:40:54,460
Subak and Don aren't the same! 

547
00:40:54,460 --> 00:40:56,460
How can you compare those two? 

548
00:41:22,260 --> 00:41:23,840
You're still up? 

